data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome in the sought-after Cypress Landing community! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence exudes charm and elegance, boasting a host of beautiful updates and amenities.    Step inside to discover a meticulously maintained interior featuring newer flooring that adds warmth and sophistication to the space.    The spacious master bedroom is a serene retreat, complete with a beautifully updated shower, providing the ultimate in relaxation and comfort. Another generously sized bedroom ensures plenty of space for family members or guests.    Outside, a sprawling backyard awaits, perfect for entertaining guests, enjoying al fresco dining, or simply unwinding amidst the lush greenery.    Conveniently located near TopGolf, the interstate, shopping, and restaurants, this townhome offers unparalleled access to all the amenities and attractions Cypress Landing has to offer.    Don't miss your chance to call this exquisite townhome yours. Schedule your showing today
